title: Game Scoop Episode 533
description: Cyberpunk 2077, Borderlands 3, Link's Awakening, Avengers, Final Fantasy 7, and so much more. The song at the end of this episode is called "Forget I Said Anything," from back when Daemon was recording under the name Monster-0.
